g/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/infrastructure/repository/entity/EntityUtils.java`\n\n**Domain Layer - Model Builders:**\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/domain/model/article/ArticleModelBuilder.java`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/domain/model/user/UserModelBuilder.java`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/domain/model/comment/CommentBuilder.java`\n- `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/domain/model/tag/TagBuilder.java`\n\n**Domain Layer - Feature Implementations (29 files):**\nAll files in `/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__realworld__jakarta__spring/run_3/output/src/main/java/org/example/realworldapi/domain/feature/impl/` including:\n- CreateUserImpl, LoginUserImpl, UpdateUserImpl, FindUserByIdImpl, FindUserByUsernameImpl\n- CreateArticleImpl, FindArticleBySlugImpl, FindArticleByIdImpl, FindArticleByAuthorAndSlugImpl, UpdateArticleBySlugImpl, DeleteArticleBySlugImpl, FindArticlesByFilterImpl, FindMostRecentArticlesByFilterImpl, FindArticleTagsImpl\n- CreateCommentImpl, FindCommentByIdAndAuthorImpl, FindCommentsByArticleSlugImpl, DeleteCommentImpl\n- CreateTagImpl, FindTagsImpl, FindTagsByNameCreateIfNotExistsImpl\n- FollowUserByUsernameImpl, UnfollowUserByUsernameImpl, IsFollowingUserImpl\n- FavoriteArticleImpl, UnfavoriteArticleImpl, ArticleFavoritesCountImpl, IsArticleFavoritedImpl\n- CreateSlugByTitleImpl\n\n### Key Changes Made:\n\n1. **Replaced Jakarta CDI annotations with Spring equivalents:**\n   - `@jakarta.inject.Singleton` → `@org.springframework.stereotype.Service`\n   - `@jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped` → `@org.springframework.stereotype.Service`\n   - `@jakarta.enterprise.context.Dependent` → `@org.springframework.stereotype.Service` (for DAOs, changed to `@Repository`)\n   - Removed `@jakarta.inject.Inject` (using constructor injection instead)\n   - `@org.eclipse.microprofile.config.inject.ConfigProperty` → `@org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Value`\n\n2. **Converted field injection to constructor injection:**\n   - Changed all `@Inject private FieldType field;` to `private final FieldType field;` \n   - Added constructors that take all dependencies as parameters\n   - This follows Spring best practices for dependency injection\n\n3. **Preserved Jakarta Persistence and Validation:**\n   - Kept `@PersistenceContext` for EntityManager injection (Spring Boot supports this)\n   - Kept all `jakarta.persistence.*` annotations (Spring Boot JPA fully supports Jakarta Persistence)\n   - Kept all `jakarta.validation.*` annotations (Spring Boot Validation fully supports Jakarta Validation)\n\nThe migration is complete for all files specified in your request. The application is now ready to run on Spring Boot instead of a Jakarta EE server!"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d8d75e0c-f395-45d5-b7d7-3f60b39c8ca5","uuid":"7b0306ac-5e0d-4b29-9036-52af17799e46"}
