{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01K6vEm4vSYcE1ybAy3d3Fdj","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I understand the core problems:\n\n1. **Tags double-wrapping**: TagsResource returns `ResponseEntity<TagsResponse>` directly — Spring Boot's default Jackson `ObjectMapper` (which is the wrapping one, being `@Primary`) serializes TagsResponse and wraps it since `WRAP_ROOT_VALUE` is enabled. The response becomes `{\"TagsResponse\": {\"tags\": []}}`. Need to either use the non-wrapping ObjectMapper for tags, or manually serialize.\n\n2. **403 on POST /api/users**: This is likely because Spring Security's path matching with `/api/users` might not work correctly when there's also a `/api/users/login` endpoint — or the issue is that the primary `ObjectMapper` with `UNWRAP_ROOT_VALUE` is being used by Spring to deserialize request bodies, which would fail because the request body `{\"user\":{\"username\":...}}` would be treated as a root-wrapped value.\n\n3. **Wrapping ObjectMapper as @Primary**: Since the wrapping ObjectMapper is `@Primary`, Spring MVC uses it by default for all HTTP message conversion. This causes problems because:\n   - Request deserialization expects root-wrapped JSON (but controllers manually use `objectMapper.writeValueAsString()` for responses)\n   - Actually, the controllers use `@RequestBody` which goes through Spring's HttpMessageConverter using the primary ObjectMapper, which has `UNWRAP_ROOT_VALUE` enabled — this would actually correctly unwrap `{\"user\": {...}}` into `NewUserRequestWrapper` if the wrapper class has `@JsonRootName(\"user\")`.\n\nLet me check the request wrapper classes to understand the deserialization:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":756,"cache_read_input_tokens":47658,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":756,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":710},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d8d75e0c-f395-45d5-b7d7-3f60b39c8ca5","uuid":"b62a271c-a7c9-49da-b06d-1ee5575faa79"}
