{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_014ctGUwzq8rqKyzabuLcdYu","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package org.example.realworldapi.application.web.model.response;\n     2→\n     3→import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonRootName;\n     4→import lombok.Getter;\n     5→import lombok.Setter;\n     6→import org.example.realworldapi.domain.model.user.User;\n     7→\n     8→@Getter\n     9→@Setter\n    10→@JsonRootName(\"profile\")\n    11→public class ProfileResponse {\n    12→\n    13→    private String username;\n    14→    private String bio;\n    15→    private String image;\n    16→    private boolean following;\n    17→\n    18→    public ProfileResponse(User user) {\n    19→        this.username = user.getUsername();\n    20→        this.bio = user.getBio();\n    21→        this.image = user.getImage();\n    22→    }\n    23→}\n    24→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d8d75e0c-f395-45d5-b7d7-3f60b39c8ca5","uuid":"5bc0101a-1ca0-44d7-a003-e01e26ffe70e"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01KDJmniermmsxgGtPExbziJ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Good. Now I understand the serialization flow:\n- Response models with `@JsonRootName` (UserResponse, ArticleResponse, CommentResponse, ProfileResponse) use the wrapping ObjectMapper explicitly in controllers via `objectMapper.writeValueAsString()`\n- Response models without `@JsonRootName` (TagsResponse, ArticlesResponse, CommentsResponse) are either returned directly (TagsResource) or use the `noWrapObjectMapper` explicitly\n\nNow let me also check the `ErrorResponse`:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1983,"cache_read_input_tokens":65037,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1983,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":238},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d8d75e0c-f395-45d5-b7d7-3f60b39c8ca5","uuid":"944920b1-7bb8-43ec-8f0c-79da514ea30c"}
