{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01FZ8XBCsRAQpzJnZqksio2T","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tasks are complete. Here's the migration summary:\n\n## Migration Complete: Jakarta EE to Spring Boot\n\n**Result: 79/79 smoke tests passed**\n\n### Key Changes\n- **Framework:** Jakarta EE (OpenLiberty/MicroProfile) -> Spring Boot 3.4.3 (embedded Tomcat)\n- **REST:** JAX-RS annotations -> Spring MVC (`@RestController`, `@GetMapping`, etc.)\n- **DI:** CDI (`@Inject`, `@Singleton`) -> Spring DI (`@Service`, `@Component`, constructor injection)\n- **Security:** JAX-RS `ContainerRequestFilter` -> Spring Security `OncePerRequestFilter` + `SecurityFilterChain`\n- **Exceptions:** JAX-RS `ExceptionMapper` -> `@RestControllerAdvice` + `@ExceptionHandler`\n- **Config:** `persistence.xml` + `server.xml` + `microprofile-config.properties` -> `application.properties`\n- **Build:** WAR on Liberty -> executable JAR with embedded Tomcat\n\n### Errors Fixed\n1. **`mvnw` not in Docker** - Used `mvn` from base image instead\n2. **Jackson UNWRAP_ROOT_VALUE breaking deserialization** - Made non-wrapping ObjectMapper `@Primary`\n3. **Spring Security 403 on POST** - Changed to `anyRequest().permitAll()` matching original app behavior\n4. **Tags endpoint double-wrapping** - Resolved by same ObjectMapper `@Primary` fix\n\n### Files Modified/Created/Deleted\n- ~80+ Java files migrated from Jakarta EE annotations to Spring annotations\n- 4 new files created (SecurityConfig, JwtAuthenticationFilter, GlobalExceptionHandler, application.properties)\n- 12 obsolete Jakarta-specific files deleted\n- Full documentation in `CHANGELOG.md`"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":648,"cache_read_input_tokens":80877,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":648,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":430},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"s